K12 CA CAVA Learning
















 Skip Navigation 






















Watch our video to see how online learning works






How is online schooling different from a traditional classroom?






Classes are led online with state-certified teachers and do not take place in a building, rather they take place online wherever there is an internet connection
Students work independently with educational materials and books sent directly to their door, including art supplies, science experiments, workbooks, and textbooks.**











