Here's What our Students and Parents Say
"Each one of my children has a different learning style, and at CAVA, they really have a chance to excel at the things that interest them most, but can take the time they need to work on the subjects that are more challenging for them."
— J. Ropke, parent of a CAVA student



"“[My teacher] She has given me every opportunity to succeed! She is always available for my questions and always lets me know I can do it. She is inspiring and a great teacher.”"
—Elijah S, 12th Grader at CAVA









