Complete the online registration form to start enrollment in our online education system, Connexus®.
Upload
Then complete the required forms and upload required documents for enrollment (such as your child's birth certificate, proof of residency, etc.).
Verify
Check Connexus regularly to verify that all your documents have been received. Once approved, you can complete the last step and confirm your student’s intent to attend!

Once your student is enrolled, your free course materials will be sent to you and your student’s teachers will be assigned!
