K12 International Academy programs






















Call:
                    855-738-5711

Enrollment consultants are available


                Enroll for Fall and Save $500 for Full-Time Students! Offer ends June 30th.
                Download our Program Guide






K12 International Academy is a fully accredited, private online K–12 school that liberates students from rigid schedules, classes that move too fast or too slow, bullying, and other factors that stand in the way of success.
                
Combining K12’s award-winning curriculum with exceptional teachers, an amazing support team, and an individualized learning plan for every student, K12 International Academy puts in motion a complete program tailored to helping your child learn in a flexible and innovative way, at his or her own pace.


                Now Enrolling for Fall Semester
            



                        Individualized Online Education
                    

                        An Individualized Learning Plan for your child sets K12 International Academy apart from other private schools.
                    



                        Award Winning Curriculum and Extensive Support
                    

                       Our curriculum is recognized as the gold standard in K–12 online education, and we surround you and your child with an amazing support team of teachers, academic coaches, and counselors.
                    



                        Career and Technical Education Pathways
                    

                       Full- and part-time high school students can explore career options and discover their passions while still in high school, giving them an advantage by earning an industry-recognized certification and being able to make an informed decision when choosing a college major.
                    



                        Full-Time and Part-Time Enrollment
                    

                       Students can enroll full-time or in one of more than 240 dynamic online courses.
                    





