 Curriculum
Award-winning Curriculum Designed for Your  Child’s SuccessOur engaging curriculum:

 Builds a solid foundation in reading, writing, and mathematics.
 Develops critical thinking and problem-solving skills.
 Adapts readily to different learning styles and paces.
 Fuels the imagination.
 Excites students about the infinite possibilities of education.

Explore the Curriculum - Get the Guide Proven Results
Preparing Students to Succeed in School–and in LifeIn a recent survey, Connections Academy families gave us high marks for helping students succeed academically and emotionally. Here’s how we scored*:95% of parents are satisfied with teachers’ helpfulness.
95% of parents agree their child is satisfied with the program.95% of parents agree that the program’s curriculum is high quality.Our graduates have been accepted to leading colleges and universities, including including the University of California Los Angeles (UCLA), Stanford University, United States Air Force Academy and many more!
See for Yourself - Learn More 
*Based on a survey of Connections Academy families conducted in February 2014 by Leo J. Shapiro and Associates.
 How to Enroll
Enroll Now for the 2014–15 School Year!Register
Complete the online registration form to start enrollment in our online education system, Connexus®.
Upload
Then complete the required forms and upload required documents for enrollment (such as your child's birth certificate, proof of residency, etc.).
Verify
Check Connexus regularly to verify that all your documents have been received. Once approved, you can complete the last step and confirm your student’s intent to attend!

Once your student is enrolled, your free course materials will be sent to you and your student’s teachers will be assigned!
